<paragraph id="8BAA6179DF26FFD81EE28B622E8AFC8C" blockId="33.[143,241,861,885]" box="[143,241,861,885]" pageId="33" pageNumber="1438">
<emphasis id="B961BD6BDF26FFD81EE28B622E8AFC8C" box="[143,241,861,885]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="1438">Remarks</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BAA6179DF26FFD81EE28BBA2FE2FC05" blockId="33.[143,1103,901,1020]" pageId="33" pageNumber="1438">This species is characterized by the following: the pronotum is reddish with a black basal band with sinuate anterior border and two anterior prolongations; the elytron is reddish testaceous with two black bands, the anterior band is arcuate, while the posterior one is sinuate.</paragraph>
